Package: ggsegMars
Title: MarsAtlas Cortical Parcellation for the 'ggseg' Ecosystem
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Athanasia Mo", "Mowinckel", , "a.m.mowinckel@psykologi.uio.no", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5756-0223"))
  )
Description: MarsAtlas cortical parcellation based on macroanatomical
    information with 41 regions per hemisphere for the 'ggseg' ecosystem.
    Provides a unified 'ggseg_atlas' object with both 2D polygon geometry and
    3D vertex indices, for use with 'ggseg' and 'ggseg3d'.
